cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM

This paper deals with image restoration using machine learning techniques, specifically deep convolutional neural networks (DCNNs). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves training the DCNN using synthetic data, which falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the use of machine learning for image restoration can also be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves graphics processing, which falls under the category of cs.GR (Graphics). Finally, the paper deals with image processing, which can be categorized under cs.MM (Multimedia).
